    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is recommended for those looking for a dedicated restoration project or a source for spare parts. The exterior shows significant wear, including heavy rust on the rocker panels, multiple deep dents, and severely peeling clear coat. Mechanically, the car requires substantial work to be roadworthy, as the engine currently runs rough and the transmission exhibits slipping. The interior has several tears in the upholstery and the dashboard is cracked from sun exposure. It is being sold strictly as-is.",
