    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Offered is an exceptional E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and an 8,000 RPM redline. This example is mechanically superlative, having received proactive rod bearing replacement, a comprehensive VANOS overhaul, and structural subframe reinforcement. Power is delivered via a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M Variable Differential Lock. The suspension remains taut with refreshed bushings and OEM dampers, preserving the chassis's neutral handling characteristics. The exterior retains its factory-original finish, while the interior features immaculate Nappa leather and a pixel-perfect instrument cluster. A documented service history and clean DME report confirm its collector-grade status.",
